Fabric Recipes
==============

Fabric Recipes are library of fabric scripts which can be used for configuration management of network of linux hosts.

Prerequisites
=============

    * Python >= 2.6: http://www.python.org
    * Fabric 1.4.1:
        easy_install fabric
                OR
        pip install fabric


Setup/Installation
==================

There is no need to set up anything. Just download and unzip the distribution or `git clone' the repo and you are ready to go!
Edit the fabfile/config.py file to change any global configuration settings

Usage
=====
Run fab -l in the base directory for a list of available commands.

